583
00:44:10,163 --> 00:44:11,564
What did I tell you, Richie?

584
00:44:11,631 --> 00:44:13,799
Next time you hit your sister,
I'm telling your father.

585
00:44:20,874 --> 00:44:22,975
In the worst way.

586
00:44:23,043 --> 00:44:24,610
Hey.

587
00:44:24,678 --> 00:44:27,947
