594
00:44:47,433 --> 00:44:49,635
You like classical music.

595
00:44:49,703 --> 00:44:51,336
Huh.

596
00:44:51,404 --> 00:44:54,139
You don't play any sports,
and you don't have a girlfriend.

597
00:44:55,675 --> 00:44:57,943
A little different for
the average high school boy.

598
00:44:58,011 --> 00:45:00,278
You have to admit.

599
00:45:00,346 --> 00:45:02,615
