628
00:46:31,270 --> 00:46:34,173
- Fuck you, black bastard.
- No, no. Fuck you, you fucking Chinese--

629
00:46:34,240 --> 00:46:36,709
- All right, all right. That's enough!
- Get the fuck off me.

630
00:46:36,776 --> 00:46:39,511
[Speaking Chinese]

631
00:46:39,579 --> 00:46:42,214
Okay, can I just get
two egg rolls, please?

632
00:46:42,281 --> 00:46:44,282
Sir.
Two egg rolls?

633
00:47:01,835 --> 00:47:03,035
Come on.

634
00:47:03,103 --> 00:47:07,539
[Speaking Chinese]

635
00:47:13,847 --> 00:47:15,748
What the fuck?
You speak Chinese?

636
00:47:15,815 --> 00:47:17,049
Yeah.

637
