My mom
always wanted me to...

638
00:47:21,420 --> 00:47:22,921
master a second language.

639
00:47:22,989 --> 00:47:28,093
She said if you learn one,
it's easier to learn...

640
00:47:28,161 --> 00:47:30,062
three or four.

641
00:47:30,130 --> 00:47:32,965
So I decided...

642
00:47:33,032 --> 00:47:36,969
why not learn the hardest language and go from there.

643
00:47:37,036 --> 00:47:38,837
Wow. Okay.

644
00:47:38,905 --> 00:47:41,306
So if you ever get around to speaking Spanish,
let me know.

645
00:47:41,374 --> 00:47:44,643
Maybe I can help you.
[Speaking Spanish]

646
00:47:44,710 --> 00:47:47,012
Oh, there we go.
He speaks Spanish.

647
00:47:47,080 --> 00:47:48,781
A little bit.
[Chuckles]

648
00:47:58,925 --> 00:48:01,693
