what happened to your mom.

649
00:48:07,333 --> 00:48:10,269
I looked at the file
and, um,

650
00:48:10,336 --> 00:48:13,172
to be honest with you,
there's really not a whole lot to work with.

651
00:48:13,239 --> 00:48:16,942
It just looks like
a random carjacking.

652
00:48:17,010 --> 00:48:18,977
Yeah, that's what
I've been told.

653
00:48:20,613 --> 00:48:23,515
I find it really inspiring that you're still looking into that.

654
00:48:23,582 --> 00:48:25,984
It could take years
before this guy turns up.

655
00:48:26,052 --> 00:48:28,586
And even then, there
are still no guarantees.

656
00:48:28,654 --> 00:48:31,357
