about my life, Teresa?

662
00:48:47,740 --> 00:48:49,875
I'm just trying to help you.

663
00:48:53,279 --> 00:48:56,548
What if I told you
I found the killer?

664
00:48:56,616 --> 00:48:58,783
What? Are you saying
you found him?

665
00:48:58,851 --> 00:49:01,487
No, no. I'm saying,
what if I did?

666
00:49:01,554 --> 00:49:03,322
Well, we would...

667
00:49:03,390 --> 00:49:05,324
bring him in and charge him.

668
00:49:06,893 --> 00:49:08,994
