you have a reputation...

737
00:53:11,971 --> 00:53:14,306
for being out there
for yourself.

738
00:53:14,374 --> 00:53:15,974
I mean,
you do know that, right?

739
00:53:16,041 --> 00:53:19,278
Really?
Oh, yeah. Mmm.

740
00:53:19,345 --> 00:53:23,782
